Will gather the forces of the strike giant
The Unions League and the Federation of national committees worker constitute Friday to strike a committee to coordinate the strike on Monday, which will last indefinitely.
On Saturday there will be a rally in protest, while on Monday - the day when the final vote to be held on the law of public health - unemployment will begin work.
Certainly this action will cause great difficulties in the transport, as this will stop completely transit rail and until 13 hours will be striking workers of the transport company collective of Budapest.
On the evening of Friday the Unions League will report on the details of their strike on Monday that take place in conjunction with the National Federation of committees worker.
It is also form the Committee on strike the League and the national trade union of train drivers that coordinated actions on Monday.
On Saturday there will be a rally of protest on Monday, while the trade unions participants on strike indefinitely, if no agreement is reached with the government.
This means that - in the day of the parliamentary vote on the law on public health - not informed about the date of the end of the strike started.
If the National Assembly disapproves the law of public health, the trade unions immediately withdrawn its call to strike.
On the other hand, if the law is adopted, will meet the committees to strike and decide on the future.
On the basis of the agenda of the National Assembly on Monday it is also possible that only vote on the law on public health in the very p.m. tickets evening, or perhaps around midnight.
As a result of the strike beginning on Monday, it will be necessary to have significant difficulties in transport: on the railways are no longer work indefinitely, for the Manana can to a part of the public transport of Budapest and more than half of the bus of the Volán.
At the same time, in many parts of the country will have closure of half of the ways of the roads.
Many trade unions and civil organisations have joined the strike, their names are updated constantly on the website of the League.
Some trade unions announced their strike indefinitely, others for time defined.
Until Thursday afternoon rail State and the free trade Union of railway workers (Sltf) could not reach an agreement even on the minimum services, although, to meet the Christmas celebrations, more and more people travelling on trains.
According to information received to date from the start of the day until 13 hours will be on strike the company employs public transport in Budapest, Budapest airport until 9 Manana, hold a strike four hours' Unions League of the electricity industry and thermal energy, trade unions educators called strike 2 and the trade union democratic educators from 2 to 8 p.m.
The association of Hungarian doctors will vote in national strike in hours alternative and the democratic trade union of workers in the health sector and social (Sdtsss) that are part of the cooperation forum of trade unions, held a warning strike of two hours.
The most important of the four demands put forward by the League is that the Government withdraw its proposal on the reform of the public health and put a new concept to a social debate.
The second demand is to introduce gradually the new way of calculating pensions which will enter into force on next.
The third is to ensure, by 2010, even in the case of pensions advanced the possibility of occupations that deserve to come to the system.
The fourth reason for the strike is that the free trade Union of railway workers (Sltf) that is part of the trade unions in League, they do not accept the proposal of the Ministry of Economics and transport on lines railway and expect a different proposal.
Political capital: in the country increases the risk for the guard Hungarian
According to the division of risk analysis (analysing division) of the political capital the activity of the guard Hungarian, constituted in August of this with the support of the movement for a better Hungary, from various points of view has increased the political risk of Hungary and of the region.
In the "warning on risks" of the Companía is written: in relation to the activity of the guard Hungarian the greatest political risk is the fact that "with the worsening of ethnic tensions between the Roma population and not Roma of Hungary, even in the short term can be violent".
The main reason for this is that the political strategy of the Hungarian guard is probably the provocation of an event of this nature - added the representative of the research institute.
Claimed that all this is due to one of the main faults of the protagonists in the political life Hungarian: "the protagonists of public life I gave the public debate of the Roma problem to the representatives of the political groupings radical and extremists, who were able to base its policy strategy on the discrepancies between Roma and Hungarians."
This makes the problem worse, prevents normal dialogue, strengthens extremists and increases the likelihood of the outbreak of violent conflicts - believe.
On top of that, according to the research institute, the activity of the National Guard, as a result of the great attention of the national average and international, "deteriorated significantly the image of Hungary abroad, especially in regard to the stability and democratic development of the country."
They remind us that: from Otono 2006 received more and more publicity and boost the reorganisation of radical groups and of extreme right in Hungary and that since the summer of 2007 have been set up in the country many organisations that of "associations of national self-defense."
"The common feature of these groups is that they define themselves as civil organisations, while the training of its members to the defence - even armed - (civil defence, national defense, protection of public order), referring to the inadequacies of the police, the army, in other words of the State" - add.
All this takes place in accordance with the method that tries to give a presentation civil different political aspirations, on the basis of the dissatisfaction of the society with politics and political parties.
Because highlight what civil and form of partnership in the case of these partnerships not only serves to avoid the legal problems of the legal status, but at the same time it is also a political strategy.
According to the analysis, the activity of the guard Hungarian is also a risk factor from the point of view of neighbourly relations.
"In recent months, in many neighbouring States referred to the Hungarian guard as a potential danger, while the political figures Ultra-nacionalistas of certain neighbouring countries, want to justify its own policy Anti-húngara with the creation of the guard Hungarian.
All this has a bearing on the political stability of the region "- incorporated.
According to the research institute, the Constitution of the Hungarian guard is not an isolated phenomenon in Central and Eastern Europe, so that throughout the region were increased the political risks.
Wrote that the guard Hungarian works in such a way that for example the national guard Bulgarian, whose constitution was announced in August 2007 for the Bulgarian national Union (Unb) of the extreme right.
The Constitution of the Bulgarian guard is due to the riots mass of gypsies that took place in one of the suburbs of Sofia (Krasna Poliana).
Taking advantage of this situation, the Unb decided to form the guard, on the grounds that the objective of the organisation is "national self-defense."
In his opinion, in the last 17 years there was "terror" Roma in Bulgaria, but the state remained powerless and unresponsive in the face of the facts - is reminiscent of the political capital.
Incorporated: this initiative has provoked a lively discussion in the Bulgarian public opinion.
As he wrote, indicates the increased risk of ethnic clashes which certain organisations Roma in Bulgaria have announced that to resist, will form its own guard.
As the operation of the Hungarian guard so far has shown similarities with the Bulgarian National Guard, can not be excluded that the Roma of Hungary react to the threat in a similar way, by organising its own self-defense - can be read in the warning about the risks of the political capital.
The director of research of the political capital, Attila Juhász to the question of the news agency said: the risk analysis is one of the activities of the research institute.
As he said, each published its risk analysis and when they experience something that can have an impact on the change of the risk, inform the public, as happened in this case, publishing its warning about the risks.
The party is not always writes with red
In Hungary the law defines precisely the days are written with red in the timetable and already has become a widespread practice that around the holidays - that the next will be less - reorganise working hours.
Even in the EU or in North America are uniform parties.
The laws Hungarian make a difference between national holiday, feast of State and days.
Hours mainly relate to Christmas religious and historical anniversaries.
The new also: both the last day of the old, as the first day of the new is festive - the latter especially for those who spent celebrating the old.
Throughout the holidays written with red in the timetable.
It is a national holiday on 15 March in memory of the revolution of 1848 and the 23 October, Memorial Day of the revolution of 1956.
On 20 August welcome the founding of the state, on 1 May or the feast of work or, on 1 and 2 November or we remember our relatives and friends who have died.
Moreover, in our country are celebrations two days the Easter of resurrection, the whit and the Christmas.
According to the timetable, our celebrations State, national or religious rarely coincide with a weekend, so often makes bridge when before or after the party there is only one working hours.
In exchange for the weekend Alargados as well, for on Saturday prior you can not leave work or school.
Is the Minister of Labour that regulates in its decree specific when work needs to be done exactly in exchange for time directly precedent or subsequent to the Party.
This rule is legal compliance compulsory for all employers and for their employees, as well as for the employees and public servants.
It is not compulsory in exchange for companies and institutions of services which, due to their role, work even during the days.
This the rules of procedure can be altered only around the end of parties: from 24 December virtually stop life in the country, because according to experience, most people "bridge" during the days between Christmas and the end of the or take their holidays during these days.
The next number of our Christmas to coincide with the middle or weekends, so there will be fewer changes in working hours which this.
First will be changed agenda on the feast of work and then, for four days, successive workers.
On Saturday, 26 April will be working hours, that in return for Friday 2 may be hours.
The other change is related to the feast of 23 October: on Saturday 18 October, we will have to work instead of 24 on Friday.
On the other hand, the next during the holiday in order to be able to rest, as from 24 December not work almost anywhere, even if the last day is a Wednesday.
