Cuba, the island more beautiful Caribbean
For Vistantes is really the island of freedom.
Anything that expect their holidays can be met, provided that Eliga correctly.
Sandy beaches and gold, large waves or a sea calm as a pond.
The palm trees and the all including waiters offering pizzas on the beach, or varied.
Kitesurfing, golf and roulette.
On the island of the Caribbean Sea can find all this and much more.
Only on an island is still much more and that island is Cuba, the largest and most beautiful of all the islands of the great Antilles.
At the time of the Spanish, Cuba became the bastion of the conquest of America.
Columbus called it, the most beautiful that human eye has seen.
Havana became warehouse and port cargo of treasures that the Spanish of America and led to Europe.
And then came the time American.
The hotel national grew at the end of the 20 years.
What sent build one of the heads of the Mafia American, Lucky Luciano, because everything that needs to be of crime in the US (and therefore prohibited) was welcome and supported in Cuba as drugs, gambling and prostitution.
Among its guests were, among others
Winston Churchill, Ava, Frank Sinatra.
In Havana arose buildings, high by floods at cars that were a symbol of worship in the 1950s of the last century.
Ernest Hemingway are bought a finance in San Francisco of Paula, near Havana, and in Cojimar was yacht.
