Cuba still offers a curious that is unique in the world and it is very valued by lovers of the railways.
Sugar cane is transported from the vast plantations until sugar factories by Vias close in machines steam or electricity.
Their garages for dozens of years were discovered and are there now, machines that work and whose models brothers in other parts of the world are only in museums.
Where to go?
The place better known for most Vistantes does not change.
