The Congress adopted the implementation of the MiFID, which entered into force on 1 November
In parallel with his parliamentary procedure, which ended today with the vote by the Congress of the amendments made to the draft in the Senate, the government has put to the public hearing that the regulation developed, with the aim of the new law that both enter into force before the end of the year.
The representatives of the various groups agreed to highlight the efforts made by Members and senators to negotiate and reach a consensus on the better regulation for the sake of ensuring the protection of investors and regulate in detail the activity of the institutions to ensure that the markets function efficiently.
The MiFID, amending the law of the stock market, is the modernisation of the financial markets, while strengthens investor protection, improving the supervisory powers of the national Commission of the stock market () and encourages cooperation between different supervisors of the European Union.
The new rules will make it possible to provide financial advisory services both signatures specialist and natural or legal persons and creates a new type of signatures of financial services (Esis), the societies of advice financial (Afi), joining the societies of values, values agencies and portfolio management companies.
In addition, it extends the number of systems for the implementation of operations on financial instruments, so that the secondary markets are regulated add together the negotiating multilateral systems and systems of internalisation of orders, which will compete with the current managers stock exchange.
The law also requires companies investment services to disseminate market information on the key aspects of his profile of business, exposure to risk and forms of risk management and required to carry a register of all transactions carry out, in order to facilitate supervision by the powerful.
In its passage through the Committee on the economy of the Congress, were incorporated several changes, which stresses that the debts Titulizadas are seen as a financial instrument "complex" because of their high risks for the investor, that has been demonstrated with what happened with the debt of subprime Americans (subprime).
Moreover, seized the transposition of the directive to define legally functions that can develop the graduates in economic and business 30 years after it was adopted in 1977 the Royal Decree which sets the functions professional reserved for economists.
For its part, the Senate included the creation of new figures in the financial sector, such as the mediator, to work in paid employment, not require the authorisation and can provide services of marketing of products and capture of customers to various investment firms at the same time.
