Sure what I should be?
motor insurance, which covers the driver to possible claims, is a major expenditure that will depend on various factors such as age, sex, age of the card, the marital status, the type of vehicle to ensure or the use of, among others.
Take the car is only the beginning.
And that is that, choose appropriate motor insurance is even more difficult to choose the model of vehicle.
First of all we must be clear what we are talking about.
Car insurance is an agreement between an insurance company and the insured.
This compromise takes the form of a contract of insurance, which states that the company will receive the value of the premium agreed in exchange for responsible for the obligation to pay compensation in the event of a disaster.
The premium is the price of insurance, which is set out in view of various factors such as age, sex, age of the card, the marital status, the type of vehicle to assure him or the use of, among others.
Insurance companies set their prices according to the statistics, so that most likely to have an accident, the greater share to pay.
It is for that reason that both the age of 25 and women have to pay premiums lower, as the statistics show that have a lower rate of accidents due to their care.
Also, lists, companies have come to the conclusion that married people tend to have fewer accidents than drivers singles.
The use of it to the vehicle will influence the frequency, and thus in the likelihood of having some sort of.
By increasing the frequency increase the odds.
There are many variables that insurers take into account when setting the price of the premium.
It is for this reason that the driver must take a good look at the situation to choose the best suited to its profile.
Here the most significant variables to choose one or other types of insurance, so that it, in addition to adapt to the characteristics of the insured, offered a reasonable price.
Young people under the age of 25 are with various disadvantages in hiring insurance at an affordable price, such as reduced experience in driving and the age of the card.
Although the ideal to be well assured is any risk insurance, there are other options economic.
More cautious drivers may choose to a risk with franchise, so get the coverage of insurance to any risk but at a price that is more feasible.
Such a Convention would mean that customers pay a part of the amount of the disaster.
"The part of the amount of the sinister that brings the customer is Preestablecerá depending on the value of the premium, which will be the higher the lower the amount", specifies Luis Noguera, maximum responsible in Spain of Europe, first mediator insurance online.
Another option is a safe third expanded, so that the customer ensuring protection against damage caused to third parties, although not the first caused in their own car.
In addition, it would be covered by theft, fire and the loss of the vehicle.
A Council.
If you are under the age of 25 years trying to be careful and avoid accidents as far as possible, as this will have an impact on the bonus, and could reduce the cost of insurance in the future.
A bonus is a reduction on the tariff basis with the company.
On the contrary, a penalty is a surcharge tariff on that basis.
"The bonuses and penalties will depend on the company and profit.
If the company has had a good year can afford to increase subsidies ", clarifies Noguera.
The Gaza last 25 years drivers are easier to take out insurance, since the rate of accidents is reduced as a result of the experience gained.
For this reason, the most desirable is to take any risk with franchise.
"Normally young people can not make use of the experience already gained in use in an accident, and even in the driving," assures the head in Spain of the European company, adding that most accidents occur in the second year of driving, once it is now the' fear of the novice'.
However, if the customer is married but does not yet have children is preferable to negotiate any risk insurance, as long as its economic situation permitting, of course.
For its part, marriages with children are viewed by insurers as the public with lowest rate of accidents, so that the surcharges will be lower.
In this case, the best would be one sure to any risk with franchise (which can be 300 Euros), or, when they have a high level of bonus, one third extended from the third year of life of the vehicle.
"Conducting a driving more relaxed and have the greatest purchasing power to afford to take a number of franchise more", ruling Luis Noguera.
For retired people is commendable insurance to any risk with franchise (and this of EUR 150), or one third extended when it has a high level of bonus.
It must be said that motor insurance is important, not only because it covers the driver to possible claims, but also because it represents an important expenditure, which is why it is essential to study properly insurance that more suits us in our personal situation.
