After a few months ago the newspaper Expressen "doubt about the authenticity of Brillo-boxes of Warhol modern Museet Stockholm made disappointing: six" Brillo-boxes ", that the Ex-director museum Pontus Hulthén gave the museum modern Museet, are false, and almost 100 of the other type of" Stockholm, "which on the road in the market, are too.
Prehistory is too complicated with a confused relationship between production and artistic Patrocionadas.
In 1964 Warhol created in New York its first "Brillo-boxes", painted wood boxes of red, blue and white, with the same shows that had cartons of soap powder "glare".
According to Warhol, in the exhibition of their works 1968 in the museum modern Museet were exposed hundreds of Brillo-cajas cardboard. These did not Warhol (as a result of the expenditure), but were brought directly from the factory cardboard "glare".
It was not a question of works of art, but of copies (which were only some objects) exposed.
In the same year, 1968, Warhol allowed to produce in Sweden a Brillo-cajas of wood, but they were not set out in the museum modern Museet.
Witnesses of those days talk now that almost fifteen boxes, which at the time entered in the history of art and the auction as the original "Brillo-boxes" type of "Stockholm" authorised by Andy Warhol.
In auctions some of them were bought by more than 100 000 dollars.
The problem is that after the famous director of the museum Pontus Hulthén made false statements that in 1968 in Sweden were produced and exposed almost 100 boxes of wood Warhol are left him.
But in reality, 105 boxes were produced in year 1990 in Malmö for Hulthén and for exposure in St. Petersburg.
In this time Warhol had already dead for three years.
Lars Byström Conservatives, the head of the museum of modern Museet, investigated six Brillo-boxes property of the Museum and also three of private property Swedish that were manufactured in 1968 in Stockholm. First and Esmerilaron their Platas serried and then the painted The with the Pincel.
On the contrary, the structure of the copies of the 1990 shows that the paint was applied with a steamroller without print directly Platas serried. In addition it is not a question of the paint, but the paint Acrílica.
"These boxes have not been authorized by the artist and must be removed from the official list of Brillo-boxes of Warhol," says Lars Nittve, the director of the museum modern Museet and adds that if the Commission of "Warhol art" in New York will not come to any conclusion, the museum modern Museet Clasificará these six boxes as copying / objects of exposure. "
Already in July the Commission of announced formally that accepts these "serious allegations" that this is boxes of soap powder.
But from that moment there all remained in absolute silence.
Soldiers rebels will be held in Manila.
In the Philippines have been paid soldiers rebels who had been entrenched in a hotel in Manila and had demanded the fall of the President Gloria Macapagal Arroyo.
The ringleader Antonio Trillanes, which accuses the President, corruption and electoral fraud, told a Reportera that it could not respond to spill blood.
Soldiers loyal to the government had broken into the hotel using tear gas.
Almost two hundred soldiers are Atrincheraban for a few hours in the building.
Almost half of them, including Trillanes, had on Thursday trial for having tried a coup in 2003 that ended in failure.
Took advantage of the negotiations, to suddenly be able to deposit with about 30 supporters.
Obviously the military police to monitor it were your ranks and followed their mutiny.
They entered the hotel "Peninsula" and demanded the fall of the President Gloria Macapagal Arroyo.
The troops of the government blocked the district in the vicinity of the hotel noble.
The President called for an urgent meeting of the security cabinet.
Norberto Gonzales, the national security adviser, condemned the behaviour of the soldiers.
"People are fed up with Trillanes," he said.
"Hold people to come to our ranks."
The general Danilo Lim, that before addressing the troops of elite scout Reangers, said that the other troops military wanted to continue the March.
The major critics of government called on Thursday at a large demonstration against the President.
For months his Government receives accusations by corruption.
In 2003 the financial district in Manila was a place that attracted all the attention by the mutiny which was tried against Arroyo.
The lifting failed after nearly 24 hours that the army wanted to participate.
Since 1986 in the Philippines have been at least seven attempts of coups against democratically elected government.
United Internet will be the largest shareholder Versatel.
United Internet assured more than 20% of the shares of the telecommunications company Versatel.
On Wednesday the company reported that the average price for an action is 14, 46 euros.
One has only 20,05 per cent of the equity capital.
There was much speculation about the takeover of the company.
There are also options for increase in the financial section Versatel.
United Internet reported that with this step to speed up the consolidation of the German market of Dsl (line of digital subscriber).
On Wednesday already made the assumptions on the entry into the business, after the Bank Brendenberg increased its participation to the operator network of Duesseldorf by 5 by hundreds to the 15,1 by hundreds.
In the financial market that means that the financial institution maintains certificates of participation to a third partner.
United Internet as early as the day before did participate with almost 10 hundreds in the company of telecommunications Drillisch.
Drillisch as far enlargement of capital put 17.4 million new actions that have a value of 106,4 million.
United Internet has bought of them 5,15 million actions by 31,4 million.
Moreover, companies began with the negotiations on partnerships trading Dsl-productos.
"We are strengthening our cooperation", explained the Potravoz of United Internet.
The two companies founded a company junta MSP, to acquire the competitor Freenet.
On Thursday United Internet reported that at the beginning, the two companies want to be pleased with the participation of ten per cent to Freenet and do not make use of its right, in other words, do involve 18,49 by hundreds of Freenet.
This meant that both companies kept all options, especially the participation in the company Freenet.
The negotiations between United Internet and Freenet on a strategic partnership ended in Mid-November.
This "game" with Freenet that will last for many months and it is not very understandable is part of the consolidation of the German market of telecom.
At the end of the third quarter Freenet had 2.9 million customers with a contract of mobile phone and 1.27 million with a contract Dsl or a contract completely.
So far the holding of United Internet and Drillisch had directly 6,01 per cent of participation in Freenet.
Then agreed that Drillisch going to achieve the other four per cent.
The right to buy 18,49 percent of the society of investment Vatas was agreed in August.
